data.description: Immerse yourself in the epitome of Florida Keys living with this impeccably designed 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in the highly sought-after neighborhood. Nestled amidst the allure of Largo Sound Village, you'll find yourself surrounded by renowned destinations and an abundance of outdoor activities. For the outdoor enthusiast, this locale offers an array of activities, including fishing, snorkeling, boating, SCUBA diving, and charters, ensuring that adventure is always at your doorstep. The home itself is a haven for both relaxation and entertainment, boasting a brand-new pool, a spacious patio deck, a charming tiki hut, a refreshing outdoor shower, and a bar perfect for creating cherished memories with family and friends. Additionally, residents of Largo Sound Village enjoy access to a private homeowner's park and boat ramp, making aquatic adventures effortlessly accessible. With quick access to the open ocean through Largo Sound and Adam's Cut just a stone's throw away, navigating the crystal-clear waters of the bay is a breeze. A newly installed A/C unit, ensuring year-round comfort. The house resides in an X flood zone, providing peace of mind for flood protection. Impact windows and doors, along with a resilient metal roof, offer the ultimate protection against Florida's ever-changing weather, features that are highly coveted in the Florida Keys. Moreover, this prime location is a mere 50-minute drive from the vibrant Miami International Airport, making both domestic and international travel exceptionally convenient. Indulge in the ultimate Florida Keys lifestyle with this turn-key residence.
